OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,FGirls in the UK are drinking, smoking
OL,7,Fand vaping more than boys, while
OL,8,FEngland is "top of the charts"
OL,9,Fglobally for child alcohol use, a
OL,10,Fmajor report has found.
OL,12,FIn one of the largest studies of its
OL,13,Fkind, the World Health Organisation
OL,14,F(WHO) examined data from 280,000
OL,15,Fchildren aged 11, 13 and 15 from 44
OL,16,Fcountries who were asked about their
OL,17,Fuse of cigarettes, vapes and alcohol.
