OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,FThe research covered youngsters living
OL,7,Fin Europe, Central Asia and Canada,
OL,8,Fand included more than 4,000 children
OL,9,Fin England, some 4,000 in Scotland and
OL,10,Fchildren in Welsh schools.
OL,12,FIt reveals that two-fifths of girls in
OL,13,FEngland and Scotland have vaped by the
OL,14,Fage of 15 - higher than in other
OL,15,Fcountries such as France, Austria,
OL,16,FGermany, Albania, Spain, Canada, and
OL,17,FNorway.
