OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,FAt the age of 11, England tops the
OL,7,Fglobal chart, with 34% of girls and
OL,8,F35% of boys saying they have drunk
OL,9,Falcohol.
OL,11,FBy 13, some 57% of girls and 50% of
OL,12,Fboys in England have drunk alcohol `
OL,13,Fagain topping the global chart.
OL,15,FChildren in Scotland and Wales are
OL,16,Falso more likely to have ever smoked
OL,17,Fcannabis than those in many other
OL,18,Fcountries.
