OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,FBoth countries are in the top five
OL,7,Fglobally. Data shows that 15-year-old
OL,8,Fboys in Scotland (23%) have the
OL,9,Fhighest rates overall for boys. Only
OL,10,Fgirls in Canada score higher (25%).
OL,12,FDr Jo Inchley, international co-
OL,13,Fordinator for the study, called Health
OL,14,FBehaviour In School-Aged Children, and
OL,15,Ffrom the University of Glasgow,
OL,16,Fsuggested some of the UK data is
OL,17,Fconcerning.
