OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,FShe said: "Vaping in the UK is higher
OL,7,Fthan the average across all the
OL,8,Fcountries that took part in the survey
OL,9,Fas a whole.
OL,11,F"I guess that's a little bit
OL,12,Fconcerning, and we've certainly seen
OL,13,Fquite marked increases in vaping in
OL,14,FScotland over the last four years...
OL,15,Flifetime use of e-cigarettes has more
OL,16,Fthan doubled in Scotland since 2018.
