OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,F"So there's two areas for concern. One
OL,7,Fis that our levels are higher than
OL,8,Felsewhere in Europe and, secondly, it
OL,9,Flooks like the trends are worsening
OL,10,Fquite substantially over a relatively
OL,11,Fshort period of time in the UK."
OL,13,FDr Inchley said one driver of
OL,14,Fincreasing vape use may be their
OL,15,Favailability and low cost.
