OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,F"Disposable vapes seem to be fairly
OL,7,Freadily accessible to young people and
OL,8,Fschools are reporting that that's a
OL,9,Fmajor issue that they're having to
OL,10,Fdeal with on a day-to-day basis. Young
OL,11,Fpeople are telling us that too.
OL,13,F"Having ready access to any kind of
OL,14,Fsubstance like that obviously makes it
OL,15,Fmore attractive and available, so that
OL,16,Fis a big issue.
