OL,3,CYoung girls in the UK drinking,
OL,4,Csmoking and vaping more than boys
OL,6,F"Some of the policy responses we're
OL,7,Fseeing now from governments across the
OL,8,FUK is really positive in that respect,
OL,9,Fbecause we do need to address the
OL,10,Fissue of availability and
OL,11,Faccessibility."
OL,13,FDr Hans Kluge, WHO regional director
OL,14,Ffor Europe, said the widespread use of
OL,15,Fharmful substances among children "is
OL,16,Fa serious public health threat".
